OL,3,C"Totally laughable and unachievable"
OL,5,FAs the government announces that
OL,6,Fdangerous cladding on high-rise
OL,7,Fbuildings to be fixed by 2029 a lease
OL,8,Fholder in Manchester has raised
OL,9,Fconcerns.
OL,11,FThe Remediation Acceleration Plan will
OL,12,Fset out that by the end of 2029, all
OL,13,Fbuildings over 18 metres tall `
OL,14,Fdefined as high-rise ` with unsafe
OL,15,Fcladding that are on a Government
OL,16,Fscheme will have been remediated.
