OL,3,C"Totally laughable and unachievable"
OL,5,FDeputy Prime Minister Angela Rayner
OL,6,Fdescribed the plans as "decisive
OL,7,Faction" and said the "pace of
OL,8,Fremediation has been far too slow for
OL,9,Ffar too long."
OL,11,FHowever, campaigners have labelled
OL,12,Fthem as "extremely disappointing"
OL,13,Fproposals that will "only make a
OL,14,Fhorribly complicated process worse".
