OL,3,C"Totally laughable and unachievable"
OL,5,FRuth Guest has owned her apartment in
OL,6,FManchester for twenty years and is
OL,7,Fdoubtful the target will be reached.
OL,8,FShe said "Like many of the
OL,9,Fleaseholders in the country I was
OL,10,Fstuck in a property that we couldn't
OL,11,Fsell. It was a zero valued property.
OL,12,FWe couldn't get a mortgage for it so
OL,13,Flife became in limbo. We couldn't do
OL,14,Fanything.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
