OL,3,C"Totally laughable and unachievable"
OL,5,F"We have had leaseholders who have had
OL,6,Fto put off their wedding plans or
OL,7,Fstarting a family. Their career
OL,8,Fprospects have been put on hold. If
OL,9,Fthey have been able to move they have
OL,10,Fbecome accidental landlords because
OL,11,Fthey cannot sell their property. It is
OL,12,Fjust crazy. It is heartbreaking.
OL,14,F"Ruth is waiting for a 'waking watch'
OL,15,Fbill - a fire safety system where
OL,16,Fsuitably trained staff continually
OL,17,Fpatrol the floors and the external
OL,18,Fperimeter of a building to maintain
OL,19,Fthe safety of occupants.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
