OL,3,C"Totally laughable and unachievable"
OL,5,FRuth said "It is crazy. Fortunately
OL,6,Ffor me I am a qualifying lease holder
OL,7,Fbecause I own less that four
OL,8,Fproperties so I have got protection up
OL,9,Fto #1000 per year. For non qualifying
OL,10,Fleaseholders who own four or more
OL,11,Fproperties they are liable for the
OL,12,Fwhole cost. We are sitting here as
OL,13,Finnocent victims.
OL,15,FI just cannot see how a 2029 deadline
OL,16,Fis achievable. Four and a half years
OL,17,Fafter the building safety fund opened
OL,18,Fwe are not really anymore forward. How
OL,19,Fare they going to achieve it in five
OL,20,Fyears? It is totally laughable and
OL,21,Funachievable.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
