OL,3,C"Totally laughable and unachievable"
OL,5,F"This is my safe haven or should be my
OL,6,Fsafe haven but every time I open my
OL,7,Fdoor I get a reminder. That 'waking
OL,8,Fwatch' walking around. A constant
OL,9,Freminder of how dangerous this
OL,10,Fbuilding is.
OL,12,FRuth management company has said it
OL,13,Fwill get in touch with Granada Reports
OL,14,Fin fifteen days. It adds it is working
OL,15,Fdiligently to remedy the issue.
OL,17,FThe announcement comes more than seven
OL,18,Fyears after the Grenfell Tower fire
OL,19,Fkilled 72 people.
